  "core_title": {
    "en": "A New Student in Cairo",
    "ja": "カイロからの新しい留学生",
    "fr": "Un nouvel étudiant au Caire",
    "ko": "카이로에서 온 새로운 학생"
  },
  "core_reading_html": {
    "en": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-hello' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"hello\", \"vocab-hello\")'>Hello</span></strong>, my <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-name' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"name\", \"vocab-name\")'>name</span></strong> is Yasmina Kamal. I am a <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-student' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"student\", \"vocab-student\")'>student</span></strong> from <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-egypt' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"egypt\", \"vocab-egypt\")'>Egypt</span></strong>. I <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-live' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"live\", \"vocab-live\")'>live</span></strong> in a small <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-flat' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"flat\", \"vocab-flat\")'>flat</span></strong> in the city of Cairo. I have a wonderful <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-family' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"family\", \"vocab-family\")'>family</span></strong> with two <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-brothers' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"brothers\", \"vocab-brothers\")'>brothers</span></strong> and one sister. Every morning, I study very hard. I want to learn English because it is a very important <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-international' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"international\", \"vocab-international\")'>international</span></strong> language for my future career. I enjoy meeting new people from different countries. <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-goodbye' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"goodbye\", \"vocab-goodbye\")'>Goodbye</span></strong> for now, and I hope you have a really nice <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-day' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"day\", \"vocab-day\")'>day</span></strong>!</p>",
    "ja": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-hello' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"こんにちは\", \"vocab-hello\")'>こんにちは</span></strong>、私の<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-name' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"なまえ\", \"vocab-name\")'>名前</span></strong>はヤスミナ・カマルです。私は<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-egypt' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"えじぷと\", \"vocab-egypt\")'>エジプト</span></strong>から来た<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-student' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"がくせい\", \"vocab-student\")'>学生</span></strong>です。今、カイロの街にある小さな<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-flat' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"あぱーと\", \"vocab-flat\")'>アパート</span></strong>に<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-live' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"すんでいます\", \"vocab-live\")'>住んで</span></strong>います。私の素敵な<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-family' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"かぞく\", \"vocab-family\")'>家族</span></strong>には二人の<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-brothers' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"きょうだい\", \"vocab-brothers\")'>兄弟</span></strong>と一人の姉妹がいます。毎日一生懸命勉強しています。英語は将来の仕事のためにとても重要な<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-international' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"こくさい的\", \"vocab-international\")'>国際的</span></strong>な言語なので、学びたいと思っています。いろいろな国の人と出会うのが大好きです。それでは<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-goodbye' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"さようなら\", \"vocab-goodbye\")'>さようなら</span></strong>、あなたにとって素晴らしい<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-day' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"いちにち\", \"vocab-day\")'>一日</span></strong>になりますように！</p>",
    "fr": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-hello' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"bonjour\", \"vocab-hello\")'>Bonjour</span></strong>, mon <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-name' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"nom\", \"vocab-name\")'>nom</span></strong> est Yasmina Kamal. Je suis une <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-student' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"étudiante\", \"vocab-student\")'>étudiante</span></strong> originaire d'<strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-egypt' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"Égypte\", \"vocab-egypt\")'>Égypte</span></strong>. Je <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-live' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"vis\", \"vocab-live\")'>vis</span></strong> dans un petit <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-flat' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"appartement\", \"vocab-flat\")'>appartement</span></strong> situé dans la ville du Caire. Ma <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-family' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"famille\", \"vocab-family\")'>famille</span></strong> est formidable et je compte deux <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-brothers' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"frères\", \"vocab-brothers\")'>frères</span></strong> et une sœur. Je travaille beaucoup chaque jour. Je veux apprendre l'anglais car c'est une langue <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-international' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"internationale\", \"vocab-international\")'>internationale</span></strong> essentielle pour mon futur métier. J'adore rencontrer des gens de cultures différentes. <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-goodbye' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"au revoir\", \"vocab-goodbye\")'>Au revoir</span></strong> et passez une excellente <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-day' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"journée\", \"vocab-day\")'>journée</span></strong> !</p>",
    "ko": "<p><strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-hello' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"안녕하세요\", \"vocab-hello\")'>안녕하세요</span></strong>, 제 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-name' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"이름\", \"vocab-name\")'>이름</span></strong>은 야스미나 카말입니다. 저는 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-egypt' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"이집트\", \"vocab-egypt\")'>이집트</span></strong>에서 온 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-student' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"학생\", \"vocab-student\")'>학생</span></strong>입니다. 저는 지금 카이로 시내의 작은 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-flat' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"아파트\", \"vocab-flat\")'>아파트</span></strong>에 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-live' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"삽니다\", \"vocab-live\")'>삽니다</span></strong>. 저희 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-family' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"가족\", \"vocab-family\")'>가족</span></strong>은 부모님과 두 명의 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-brothers' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"남자형제\", \"vocab-brothers\")'>남자형제</span></strong>, 그리고 자매 한 명으로 구성되어 있습니다. 저는 매일 열심히 공부합니다. 영어는 제 미래의 직업을 위해 매우 중요한 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-international' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"국제적인\", \"vocab-international\")'>국제적인</span></strong> 언어이기 때문에 배우고 싶습니다. 다양한 나라의 사람들을 만나는 것을 즐깁니다. 그럼 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-goodbye' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"안녕히계세요\", \"vocab-goodbye\")'>안녕히계세요</span></strong>, 정말 좋은 <strong><span class='vocab-link' id='text-day' onclick='speakAndScroll(\"하루\", \"vocab-day\")'>하루</span></strong> 보내시길 바랍니다!</p>"
  },
